<LanguageData>
  <!-- 设置与重启提示 -->
  <PCA_Settings_Category>Piped CE Autoloaders</PCA_Settings_Category>
  <PCA_Settings_Restart_Message>Piped CE Autoloaders 设置已保存。重启 RimWorld 后新的网络配置才会生效。</PCA_Settings_Restart_Message>
  <PCA_Settings_RestartNow>立即重启</PCA_Settings_RestartNow>
  <PCA_Settings_Later>稍后</PCA_Settings_Later>
  <PCA_Settings_Restart_Title>需要重启</PCA_Settings_Restart_Title>

  <!-- 网络配置 -->
  <PCA_Settings_Overview>每种颜色的网络仅输送一种指定的 Combat Extended 弹药，并可分别设置装填速度和弹药库容量。更改将在重启 RimWorld 后生效。</PCA_Settings_Overview>
  <PCA_Settings_RebindingWarning>重启后，网络中已储存的弹药和自动装载机内的弹药将采用新的弹药绑定，输入口筛选条件也会自动更新。降低容量前请先清空弹药库。</PCA_Settings_RebindingWarning>
  <PCA_Settings_AmberNetwork>琥珀色网络</PCA_Settings_AmberNetwork>
  <PCA_Settings_BlueNetwork>蓝色网络</PCA_Settings_BlueNetwork>
  <PCA_Settings_GreenNetwork>绿色网络</PCA_Settings_GreenNetwork>
  <PCA_Settings_AmmoSet>口径</PCA_Settings_AmmoSet>
  <PCA_Settings_ExactRound>弹药类型</PCA_Settings_ExactRound>
  <PCA_Settings_ReloadSpeed>换弹速度：{0}x</PCA_Settings_ReloadSpeed>
  <PCA_Settings_ReloadSpeedTooltip>数值越高，相邻炮塔的换弹速度越快。</PCA_Settings_ReloadSpeedTooltip>
  <PCA_Settings_MagazineCapacity>弹药库容量：{0}</PCA_Settings_MagazineCapacity>
  <PCA_Settings_MagazineCapacityTooltip>此网络中的每座弹药库最多可储存多少发弹药。</PCA_Settings_MagazineCapacityTooltip>

